==========================================================================

- Add support for other filesystems like extX, exfat, VFAT, FAT16/32, minix...
- Executable formats (pe, coff, a.out, ...)
- Implement UEFI support
  * Implement libefi from scratch.
- Non x86 support (arm, mips, ...)
- Multiboot specification
- Long mode support
- Implement sector-by-sector reading in CHS mode in stage1
- Add support for windows (generate documentation)
- Change style of html and pdflaTex (like RBIL)
- More support for documentation types
- Organize all '.rst' documents.
